title: UNICEF stands ready for Hurricane Patricia (Australian Committee for UNICEF Ltd)
text: ( Source : Australian Committee for UNICEF Ltd) UNICEF Australia stands with the global UNICEF community, ready to support the needs of children and their families in the wake of Hurricane Patricia . The category five major storm is expected
